{"tid":2500110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612捐款2億但律師費收左成億元 可否收平D?","createTime":"2021-04-22T11:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T11:45:35.000Z","uid":130385,"like":19,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5c16a7444d3e4c401a25f564c688d5b05aeb880a","tid":2500110,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"我預左負評一定多  但係果d咩情緒費乜乜借錢果d全部唔理<br />\n捐款2億 律師費用左1億  佔左成50%<br />\n<a href=\"https://612fund.hk/zh/latest-report\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F612fund.hk%2Fzh%2Flatest-report&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=09c75ccc\" target=\"_blank\">https://612fund.hk/zh/latest-report</a><br />\n基金會以出庭代表的律師的人數而非所代表的被告數目為基礎,資助每位律師/大律師的費用為6,000 元(半日計),或12,000 元(全日計)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.civicparty.hk/articles/612%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E8%BF%91%E5%86%B5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.civicparty.hk%2Farticles%2F612%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%2586%25B5%2F&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=6fee5e2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.civicparty.hk/articles/612%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E8%BF%91%E5%86%B5/</a><br />\n就過去兩星期收到的單據顯示，基金資助的被告人數已升至528 人，其中包括約100 人還押。<br />\n上年3月就5百幾人  我當依家一千,平均每名手足的律師費就要十萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你一年會唔會全職只係做一名手足案件先?  仲未計可能一個代表幾個果D案件拉高個平均成本<br />\n上面唔係計出庭果日先收12000蚊  如果唔係早就處理左幾千幾單案  一半手足案都處理完啦<br />\n如果佢地係每日收費 一個月單單做手足案10日就收12萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n1億先幫到一千人  依家過萬人咪要10億以上 姐係要比成5億律師費?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家理性討論12000一日合唔合理   如果收4000蚊一日d律師係咪要訓街  無錢開飯?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d19e27d4908db03f7ea6668b4eb4bb928a3e0fb","tid":2500110,"uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":7,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"樓主你走先<br />\n泛民狗衝入嚟啦<br />\n我幫你頂住"},{"pid":"a1d82ee337a1c3129f7f994ebae01abb9c01a84b","tid":2500110,"uid":130385,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d19e27d4908db03f7ea6668b4eb4bb928a3e0fb","tid":2500110,"uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":7,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:27:45.000Z","msg":"樓主你走先<br />\n泛民狗衝入嚟啦<br />\n我幫你頂住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入黎屌12000蚊太平  收夠2萬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f028917c50896f90d9ec6b0a65798784b717dd3","tid":2500110,"uid":339805,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:28:56.000Z","msg":"無錯，律師反正做呢d案都唔係為錢架啦<br />\n根本應該要成本價接case先係<br />\n食人血饅頭可恥"},{"pid":"8b42806b6f52eb55196e259384bf99c5b1e8611a","tid":2500110,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:29:02.000Z","msg":"食家有過萬人被人告咩on9仔"},{"pid":"1f3f3d11fdfb6f7f0b3d860b80b05cb1dad3ad43","tid":2500110,"uid":146351,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYocBqv2ubpXejcSzgF1WPRtdBtUz4GLmu1N7QNYyGoXM?filename=sw4fhD8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsw4fhD8.gif&h=d5cdd695&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efc9d7c8204dbc848be4ac6b3ba0d0feaa973b91","tid":2500110,"uid":123774,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZmKtTD3FBzsm1XqF3SXw4JgAs9jNS4W1KMX1EsSaJwDU?filename=zrWdOL4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzrWdOL4.png&h=34adbb57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b067df354eac5ea3eb2f9dc4c82d38803e001120","tid":2500110,"uid":172190,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:29:39.000Z","msg":"律師要養家，手足唔洗"},{"pid":"853d8bba776f292e553034d98a23c24cd14645fd","tid":2500110,"uid":53498,"like":4,"disl